SetGPUFanCurve.sh

PURPOSE: A simple script for changing Fan Curve & Other Setting on the AMD RX 7900 XTX 

I wrote this script to allow me to control the fan speed on my Sapphire Nitro+ Radeon RX 7900 XTX 24GB GDDR6 Video Card on my Gentoo Linux OS.  Thought it might be useful to others so I threw it up here.  If you want to change the various profile settings, the 'PROFILE DEFINITIONS' section should be fairly self-explanatory 

Free to use, copy, extend, fork with attribution.  Cheers


